He told me not to.

74
00:07:59,770 --> 00:08:01,981
He didn't want to worry you.

75
00:08:02,064 --> 00:08:04,192
He didn't tell me either.

76
00:08:06,736 --> 00:08:07,820
My poor boy.

77
00:08:11,449 --> 00:08:14,035
