LEE HONG-JO, GREENWAY BUILDING DIVISION

81
00:09:26,107 --> 00:09:27,108
Hong-jo.

82
00:09:27,692 --> 00:09:28,609
Are you inside?

83
00:09:31,028 --> 00:09:31,862
Hong-jo.

84
00:09:40,913 --> 00:09:43,874
I was worried.
Your phone rang, but you didn't pick up.

85
